            "title": "Co-Circulation and Excretion Dynamics of Diverse Rubula- and Related Viruses in Egyptian Rousette Bats from South Africa",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Marinda",
                    "lastName": "Mortlock"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
